  "Description": {
    "English": "Creates an antimatter field around the shots of the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Boltcaster</span>, causing them to be repelled by non-damaged surfaces.<br><br>Enables <span class=\"name name-stellar\">ricochet</span>, causing projectiles to bounce if they hit a target they do not damage.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "在<span class=\"name name-technology\">离子闪电发射器</span>的炮弹周围创造一个反物质场，使它们被未受损的表面斥回。<br><br>启用<span class=\"name name-stellar\">弹射</span>，使射弹在击中一个未造成伤害的目标时反弹。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "在<span class=\"name name-technology\">雷霆砲</span>射彈的四周製造出反物質力場，射彈碰上未毀損的表面就會反彈。<br><br>造成<span class=\"name name-stellar\">反射效果</span>，如果射彈打中目標但未造成損害，就會反彈。"
  },
